What are the main advantages of using social media marketing in a plan for digital marketing?

1- Raise brand visibility: By reaching a wider audience and boosting brand exposure.

2-Community Building and Engagement: Promote face-to-face communication to create a devoted virtual community.                  

3-Cost-Effective Advertising: Use social media advertising to target audiences while allocating money effectively.

4-Data-Driven Decision Making: Gain insightful knowledge about audience behaviour and marketing effectiveness by utilising analytics.

5-Real-Time Communication: Quickly respond to consumer questions to improve satisfaction and reputation of the brand.

